{"tid":1830063,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【邊個買呢？】成龍合體李寧搞時裝 到巴黎時裝周做生招牌","createTime":"2020-01-19T09:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T12:02:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"52790e51bb07b7f1d0ccaccbb3cda584b7f95a83","tid":1830063,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:54:18.000Z","msg":"中國前體操選手李寧退役後，進軍商界，又踩入時裝界開拓新事業，近日他聯同演員成龍搞crossover，推出新時裝系列，並在巴黎時裝周中展出。日前才在大陸為主演新片《急先鋒》宣傳的成龍，原來已飛抵巴黎，並親自為新系列時裝行騷。<br />\n<br />\n李寧的時裝騷於巴黎時間18日登場，穿上新裝的男模特兒輪流上場，其中一人面上寫有「升」字，成龍壓軸登場，他現身後攤開雙手接受觀眾掌聲，隨時他拖着李寧現身，兩人擁抱又用力握手，似乎對新合作甚有信心。<br />\n<br />\n而今次李寧除了有成龍任嘉賓之外，他更帶了退休NBA籃球員韋迪（Dwyane Wade）到場睇騷，身高2.1米的獲迪在與李寧及成龍等人自拍時，負責揸機，難怪李寧在微博貼出照片後留言說：「來巴黎看李寧時裝秀，帶一位大長手朋友的好處。」據知，今次李寧crossover成龍的時裝系列名為「功夫系列」，希望透過中國功夫表達傳統文化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200119/large/1579424604_578f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579424604_578f.jpg&h=86520531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200119/large/1579424602_b014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579424602_b014.jpg&h=2e4e4bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200119/large/1579424604_6b29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579424604_6b29.jpg&h=59a545c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200119/MH4XHRADLRSH4SVLXZBVCI554A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200119%2FMH4XHRADLRSH4SVLXZBVCI554A%2F&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=e5ebfbce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.co